不是你想的那樣  我想阻止他來著
It's not what you think. I tried to stop it.

90
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:19,460
我不知道
I didn't know--

91
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:21,400
我不想聽你
What I don't want to hear from you--

92
