那具尸體不是詹姆斯·達莫迪的
that the body was not that of James Darmody?

137
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,090
不是認為
Not an opinion.

138
00:07:42,370 --> 00:07:44,010
你說什么
I beg your pardon?

139
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:46,300
不是認為
It was not an opinion.

140
00:07:47,230 --> 00:07:48,860
我曾跟他并肩作戰
I fought beside him.

141
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:51,600
這種事是忘不掉的
You don't forget that.

142
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,670
