請求法庭原諒
begging the pardon of the court,

146
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:06,690
我昨晚才收到案件細節
I only received the particulars of this case last--

147
00:08:08,010 --> 00:08:09,950
我注意到你戴了眼鏡
I notice you're wearing glasses,

148
