眼鏡能抵住面具
They keep my face on.

156
00:08:41,970 --> 00:08:42,970
好的
Yes, all right.

157
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:45,510
那么我們能相信
So are we to believe

158
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:48,090
你的那只好眼的眼力
that the vision of your remaining eye...

159
00:08:48,090 --> 00:08:49,260
