...is more reliable than that of Mr. Darmody's own mother?

161
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,590
我知道是怎么回事
I know what happened.

162
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,390
我知道我看到了什么
I know what I saw.

163
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:58,620
我知道
I know.

164
00:08:58,620 --> 00:09:01,700
法官大人  已經頒發了一張有效的死亡證明
Your Honor, a duly certified death record has already--

165
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:03,840
是動過手腳的死亡證明  法官大人
A jerry-rigged death record, Your Honor.

166
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:06,140
而且我的委托人
And surely my client's veracity

167
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:08,140
-在辨認自己孩子這事上...  -根本沒有尸體
- as to the identity of her own child... - There's no body.

