Mr. Drake, keep your client in check or I'll have her removed.

175
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:26,590
那是我兒子  我之前說過什么都不重要
It was my son. It doesn't matter what I said.

176
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:28,010
沒有別人
There's no one there.

177
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:34,880
我在戀愛  我受了欺騙
I was in love. I was tricked.

178
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:37,040
