How can that be right?

179
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,380
你好  打擾一下
Hello. Excuse me!

180
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:42,740
不許我說話  不許我活
I'm not allowed to speak. I'm not allowed to live.

181
00:09:44,460 --> 00:09:45,130
快接線
Get on the wire.

182
00:09:45,130 --> 00:09:47,770
憑什么男人想干什么就能干什么
Why does a man get to do anything he wants?

183
00:09:47,770 --> 00:09:48,880
巾幗英雄
That a girl!

184
00:09:49,310 --> 00:09:51,160
她瘋了  尸體在哪里
She's off! Where's the body? -

